3685:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32wbxx_ll_adc.h ****   *           sequencer length and each rank affectation to a channel
3686:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32wbxx_ll_adc.h ****   *           are configurable.
