5756:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32wbxx_ll_adc.h **** /**
5757:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32wbxx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC analog watchdog monitored channels:
