6111:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32wbxx_ll_adc.h **** /**
6112:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32wbxx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC analog watchdog thresholds value of both thresholds
