6356:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32wbxx_ll_adc.h ****   *
6357:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32wbxx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (1) On STM32WB series, parameter not available on devices: STM32WB10xx, STM32WB15xx, ST
