6713:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32wbxx_ll_adc.h ****   * @rmtoll CR       ADDIS          LL_ADC_IsDisableOngoing
6714:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32wbxx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  ADCx ADC instance
