1906:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   * @brief  Enable ADC, start conversion of regular group with interruption.
1907:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   * @note   Interruptions enabled in this function according to initialization
1908:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   *         setting : EOC (end of conversion), EOS (end of sequence),
1909:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   *         OVR overrun.
1910:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   *         Each of these interruptions has its dedicated callback function.
1911:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   * @note   To guarantee a proper reset of all interruptions once all the needed
1912:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   *         conversions are obtained, HAL_ADC_Stop_IT() must be called to ensure
1913:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   *         a correct stop of the IT-based conversions.
1914:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   * @note   By default, HAL_ADC_Start_IT() does not enable the End Of Sampling
1915:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   *         interruption. If required (e.g. in case of oversampling with trigger
1916:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   *         mode), the user must:
1917:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   *          1. first clear the EOSMP flag if set with macro __HAL_ADC_CLEAR_FLAG(hadc, ADC_FLAG_EO
1918:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   *          2. then enable the EOSMP interrupt with macro __HAL_ADC_ENABLE_IT(hadc, ADC_IT_EOSMP)
1919:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   *          before calling HAL_ADC_Start_IT().
1920:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   * @param hadc ADC handle
1921:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   * @retval HAL status
1922:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_adc.c ****   */
